The chat contains a single message from user Chen0xA3 reporting an issue with their agent's tweet replies. Despite configuring their character and prompt to avoid crypto/meme/NFT content, the bot frequently includes such topics in responses. These replies appear unrelated to the original tweets being responded to (which are typically about delivery complaints from services like USPS/Amazon). Chen0xA3 questions whether this behavior might be influenced by the Twitter account's existing history, such as past tweets, likes, or follows. No responses or solutions are present in this chat segment.
